    "title": "🏛️ WILSY OS - Boardroom Narrative Dashboard",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "30s",
    "theme": "dark",
    "schemaVersion": 36,
    "version": 1,
    "panels": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "title": "Institutional Executive Summary",
        "id": 1,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### 🏛️ Executive Summary Statement\nWilsy OS demonstrates **Institutional Finality** across all sovereign pillars. By unifying SLA reliability, regulatory compliance, and green-efficiency throughput, the Citadel provides a self-healing infrastructure that neutralizes operational risk before it reaches the ledger. This summary provides the Board with absolute clarity on our trajectory toward multi-billion-dollar scale."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "title": "Sovereign Risk Highlights Index",
        "id": 2,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_risks_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "Risk Level" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": { "align": "center", "displayMode": "color-background" },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
                { "color": "#d4af37", "value": 3 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 7 }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "table",
        "title": "Strategic Opportunity Map",
        "id": 3,
        "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_opportunities_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "Growth Potential" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": { "align": "center", "displayMode": "color-text" },
            "color": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Sovereign Narrative KPI Trends (Institutional Velocity)",
        "id": 4,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 24, "h": 10 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_sla_score{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "SLA Score" },
          { "expr": "wilsy_compliance_ratio{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "Compliance" },
          { "expr": "wilsy_sustainability_index{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "ESG Index" },
          { "expr": "wilsy_efficiency_index{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}", "legendFormat": "Efficiency" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "fillOpacity": 15,
              "lineWidth": 2
            }
          }
        },
        "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "title": "Boardroom Narrative Finality Overlay",
